headline.main: Prosecutor: Missing French Family Killed With a Crowbar
headline.print_headline: Prosecutor: Missing French Family Killed With a Crowbar

lead_paragraph: The brother-in-law of a missing French couple has confessed to killing them and their two adult children with a crowbar, then dismembering the corpses, over an old inheritance dispute, authorities said Monday.
